  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The investigators propose to survey the frequency of HER2 (+) CTC in order to lay groundwork
      for future clinical trials incorporating Her-2 targeted agents in gastric cancer.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      We propose to survey the frequency of HER2 (+) CTC in order to lay groundwork for future
      clinical trials incorporating Her-2 targeted agents in gastric cancer. Blood samples will be
      collected from metastatic gastric cancer patients.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
